fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.config

Interface ImmutableConfig

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Config
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseBlueprintsConfig, BaseConfig, BerkeleyDbConfig, BlueprintsNeo4jConfig, BlueprintsTinkerConfig, HBaseConfig, InMemoryConfig, MapDbConfig, MongoDbConfig

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface ImmutableConfig
    An immutable configuration that defines the behavior of BackendFactories and StoreFactory.
